\tDual analytics tracking\t3 min 8\tCreate content structure\tPosts → New Post → Set tags/authors\tContent + metadata\tPublished article with tracking\tOngoing 9\tSubmit to search\tGoogle Search Console → Add property\tVerify ownership\tSitemap indexed\t10 min 10\tLLM optimization\tCreate /llms.txt file via code injection\tCrawl instructions\tEnhanced AI discoverability\t5 min Next Steps Confirm platform choice - Want me to build out complete implementation SOPs for any of the top 3? Schema templates - I can provide custom JSON-LD templates optimized for your content types (courses, products, articles) LLM.txt file - New standard for AI crawler instructions - want me to draft this for your chosen platform? What direction do you want to go? what are JSON-LD templates optimized for your content types JSON-LD Templates Optimized for Your Content Types Knowledge Base Update Document ID: KB-BLOG-PLATFORMS-001 Added Section: JSON-LD Schema Templates Updated: December 15, 2025 What JSON-LD Actually Does (Quick Context) JSON-LD (JavaScript Object Notation for Linked Data) is structured data markup that tells search engines and LLMs exactly what your content is. Think of it as a machine-readable summary card that sits invisibly in your page header. Why it matters for LLM indexing: ChatGPT, Claude, Perplexity, and Google's AI Overviews all prioritize content they can parse cleanly. JSON-LD gives them structured hooks to understand and cite your content. Your Content Types → Matched Schema Templates Based on your profile (SaaS founder, course creator, ecommerce, journalist/author), here are the 5 core templates you need: Template 1: Online Course / Digital Product Copy { \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\", \"@type\": \"Course\", \"name\": \"YOUR COURSE TITLE\", \"description\": \"Comprehensive description of what students learn (150-300 chars)\", \"provider\": { \"@type\": \"Organization\", \"name\": \"YOUR BRAND NAME\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com\", \"logo\": \"https://yourdomain.com/logo.png\" }, \"instructor\": { \"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"YOUR NAME\", \"jobTitle\": \"Course Creator / Founder\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com/about\" }, \"courseCode\": \"COURSE-SKU-001\", \"educationalLevel\": \"Beginner / Intermediate / Advanced\", \"teaches\": [ \"Skill 1 students will learn\", \"Skill 2 students will learn\", \"Skill 3 students will learn\" ], \"numberOfCredits\": \"0\", \"occupationalCredentialAwarded\": \"Certificate of Completion\", \"hasCourseInstance\": { \"@type\": \"CourseInstance\", \"courseMode\": \"Online\", \"courseWorkload\": \"PT10H\", \"instructor\": { \"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"YOUR NAME\" } }, \"offers\": { \"@type\": \"Offer\", \"price\": \"297.00\", \"priceCurrency\": \"USD\", \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com/course-sales-page\", \"validFrom\": \"2025-01-01\" }, \"aggregateRating\": { \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\", \"ratingValue\": \"4.8\", \"reviewCount\": \"127\", \"bestRating\": \"5\", \"worstRating\": \"1\" }, \"image\": \"https://yourdomain.com/course-thumbnail.jpg\" } Copy Field\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tWhy It Matters name\tYour exact course title\tLLMs cite this title verbatim\tAccuracy in AI responses teaches\tArray of 3-5 specific skills\tFeatured in AI course recommendations\tPerplexity/ChatGPT match queries to skills offers.price\tNumerical price\tRich snippets show pricing\t35% higher CTR with price visibility aggregateRating\tYour real ratings\tStar ratings in search\tSocial proof in SERPs courseWorkload\tISO 8601 duration (PT10H = 10 hours)\tDuration shown in results\tSets expectations, improves conversion Template 2: SaaS Product / Software Application Copy { \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\", \"@type\": \"SoftwareApplication\", \"name\": \"YOUR SAAS PRODUCT NAME\", \"description\": \"One-sentence value proposition (under 160 chars)\", \"applicationCategory\": \"BusinessApplication\", \"operatingSystem\": \"Web Browser, iOS, Android\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com\", \"author\": { \"@type\": \"Organization\", \"name\": \"YOUR COMPANY NAME\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com\", \"logo\": \"https://yourdomain.com/logo.png\", \"sameAs\": [ \"https://twitter.com/yourbrand\", \"https://linkedin.com/company/yourbrand\", \"https://youtube.com/@yourbrand\" ] }, \"offers\": { \"@type\": \"AggregateOffer\", \"lowPrice\": \"0\", \"highPrice\": \"99\", \"priceCurrency\": \"USD\", \"offerCount\": \"3\", \"offers\": [ { \"@type\": \"Offer\", \"name\": \"Free Plan\", \"price\": \"0\", \"priceCurrency\": \"USD\" }, { \"@type\": \"Offer\", \"name\": \"Pro Plan\", \"price\": \"29\", \"priceCurrency\": \"USD\" }, { \"@type\": \"Offer\", \"name\": \"Enterprise Plan\", \"price\": \"99\", \"priceCurrency\": \"USD\" } ] }, \"aggregateRating\": { \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\", \"ratingValue\": \"4.7\", \"reviewCount\": \"342\", \"bestRating\": \"5\" }, \"featureList\": [ \"Feature 1 description\", \"Feature 2 description\", \"Feature 3 description\", \"Feature 4 description\" ], \"screenshot\": [ \"https://yourdomain.com/screenshot1.png\", \"https://yourdomain.com/screenshot2.png\" ], \"softwareVersion\": \"2.5.0\", \"releaseNotes\": \"https://yourdomain.com/changelog\" } Copy Field\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tWhy It Matters applicationCategory\tBusinessApplication, FinanceApplication, etc.\tCategorized in software comparisons\tLLMs categorize for \"best X software\" queries featureList\tArray of key features\tFeatures cited in AI comparisons\tDirect answer to \"what does X do?\" offers (AggregateOffer)\tAll pricing tiers\tFull pricing shown in snippets\tAnswers pricing questions without click sameAs\tSocial profile URLs\tConnected entity graph\tStronger knowledge graph presence Template 3: Blog Article / How-To Guide Copy { \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\", \"@type\": \"Article\", \"mainEntityOfPage\": { \"@type\": \"WebPage\", \"@id\": \"https://yourdomain.com/blog/article-slug\" }, \"headline\": \"Your Article Title (Max 60 chars for display)\", \"description\": \"Meta description summarizing the article (150-160 chars)\", \"image\": { \"@type\": \"ImageObject\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com/article-featured-image.jpg\", \"width\": 1200, \"height\": 630 }, \"author\": { \"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"YOUR NAME\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com/about\", \"jobTitle\": \"Founder / Author\", \"sameAs\": [ \"https://twitter.com/yourhandle\", \"https://linkedin.com/in/yourprofile\" ] }, \"publisher\": { \"@type\": \"Organization\", \"name\": \"YOUR BRAND\", \"logo\": { \"@type\": \"ImageObject\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com/logo.png\", \"width\": 600, \"height\": 60 } }, \"datePublished\": \"2025-12-15T08:00:00+00:00\", \"dateModified\": \"2025-12-15T10:30:00+00:00\", \"articleSection\": \"Category Name\", \"keywords\": [\"keyword 1\", \"keyword 2\", \"keyword 3\"], \"wordCount\": \"2500\", \"timeRequired\": \"PT12M\", \"speakable\": { \"@type\": \"SpeakableSpecification\", \"cssSelector\": [\".article-headline\", \".article-summary\"] }, \"isAccessibleForFree\": true, \"about\": { \"@type\": \"Thing\", \"name\": \"Primary Topic of Article\" } } Copy Field\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tWhy It Matters dateModified\tISO timestamp of last update\t\"Updated X days ago\" display\tFresh content ranks higher in AI speakable\tCSS selectors for key content\tVoice assistant compatibility\tAlexa/Google Home can read your content timeRequired\tISO duration (PT12M = 12 min read)\tRead time in snippets\tSets user expectations about\tPrimary entity/topic\tTopic clustering for LLMs\tSemantic relationship building Template 4: Ecommerce Product Copy { \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\", \"@type\": \"Product\", \"name\": \"PRODUCT NAME\", \"description\": \"Detailed product description (200-500 chars)\", \"sku\": \"PROD-SKU-001\", \"gtin13\": \"1234567890123\", \"brand\": { \"@type\": \"Brand\", \"name\": \"YOUR BRAND NAME\" }, \"image\": [ \"https://yourdomain.com/product-image-1.jpg\", \"https://yourdomain.com/product-image-2.jpg\", \"https://yourdomain.com/product-image-3.jpg\" ], \"offers\": { \"@type\": \"Offer\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com/product-page\", \"price\": \"49.99\", \"priceCurrency\": \"USD\", \"priceValidUntil\": \"2025-12-31\", \"availability\": \"https://schema.org/InStock\", \"itemCondition\": \"https://schema.org/NewCondition\", \"seller\": { \"@type\": \"Organization\", \"name\": \"YOUR STORE NAME\" }, \"shippingDetails\": { \"@type\": \"OfferShippingDetails\", \"shippingRate\": { \"@type\": \"MonetaryAmount\", \"value\": \"0\", \"currency\": \"USD\" }, \"deliveryTime\": { \"@type\": \"ShippingDeliveryTime\", \"handlingTime\": { \"@type\": \"QuantitativeValue\", \"minValue\": \"1\", \"maxValue\": \"2\", \"unitCode\": \"DAY\" }, \"transitTime\": { \"@type\": \"QuantitativeValue\", \"minValue\": \"3\", \"maxValue\": \"5\", \"unitCode\": \"DAY\" } }, \"shippingDestination\": { \"@type\": \"DefinedRegion\", \"addressCountry\": \"US\" } } }, \"aggregateRating\": { \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\", \"ratingValue\": \"4.6\", \"reviewCount\": \"89\" }, \"review\": [ { \"@type\": \"Review\", \"author\": { \"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"Customer Name\" }, \"reviewRating\": { \"@type\": \"Rating\", \"ratingValue\": \"5\" }, \"reviewBody\": \"Actual customer review text here...\" } ], \"category\": \"Product Category > Subcategory\", \"material\": \"Material type if applicable\", \"weight\": { \"@type\": \"QuantitativeValue\", \"value\": \"1.5\", \"unitCode\": \"LBR\" } } Copy Field\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tWhy It Matters shippingDetails\tComplete shipping info\t\"Free shipping, 3-5 days\" in results\tGoogle Shopping requires this now review\tActual customer reviews\tReview snippets in SERPs\tTrust signals directly in search priceValidUntil\tExpiration date\tUrgency indicator\tPrompts action, validates pricing gtin13\tUPC/barcode number\tProduct matching across platforms\tGoogle product graph matching Template 5: Author/Personal Brand (For Your Profile Pages) Copy { \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\", \"@type\": \"Person\", \"name\": \"YOUR FULL NAME\", \"alternateName\": \"Common nickname or pen name\", \"description\": \"Brief bio (150-200 chars)\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com\", \"image\": \"https://yourdomain.com/headshot.jpg\", \"jobTitle\": \"SaaS Founder & Digital Marketing Strategist\", \"worksFor\": { \"@type\": \"Organization\", \"name\": \"YOUR COMPANY\", \"url\": \"https://yourdomain.com\" }, \"alumniOf\": { \"@type\": \"CollegeOrUniversity\", \"name\": \"University Name\" }, \"knowsAbout\": [ \"SaaS Growth\", \"Digital Marketing\", \"Ecommerce\", \"Copywriting\", \"Course Creation\", \"Content Strategy\" ], \"sameAs\": [ \"https://twitter.com/yourhandle\", \"https://linkedin.com/in/yourprofile\", \"https://youtube.com/@yourchannel\", \"https://instagram.com/yourhandle\" ], \"hasOccupation\": [ { \"@type\": \"Occupation\", \"name\": \"SaaS Founder\" }, { \"@type\": \"Occupation\", \"name\": \"Digital Marketer\" }, { \"@type\": \"Occupation\", \"name\": \"Author\" } ], \"award\": [ \"Award or recognition 1\", \"Award or recognition 2\" ], \"memberOf\": { \"@type\": \"Organization\", \"name\": \"Industry Association\" } } Copy Field\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tWhy It Matters knowsAbout\tYour expertise areas\tExpertise cited in AI answers\t\"According to [name], an expert in...\" sameAs\tAll verified social profiles\tKnowledge panel connections\tUnified identity across platforms hasOccupation\tMultiple roles\tMulti-faceted professional identity\tLLMs understand you're multi-disciplinary award\tRecognition, press mentions\tAuthority signals\tE-E-A-T signals for Google and LLMs Implementation Flowchart Copy ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │                      JSON-LD IMPLEMENTATION WORKFLOW                         │ ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤ │                                                                              │ │  STEP 1: Identify Page Type                                                 │ │     │                                                                        │ │     ├──► Homepage ──────────► Organization + Person Schema                  │ │     ├──► Product Page ──────► Product Schema                                │ │     ├──► Course Page ───────► Course Schema                                 │ │     ├──► Blog Post ─────────► Article Schema                                │ │     └──► About Page ────────► Person Schema                                 │ │                                                                              │ │  STEP 2: Populate Template                                                  │ │     │                                                                        │ │     └──► Fill all required fields                                           │ │         └──► Validate at schema.org/docs/validator                          │ │             └──► Test at search.google.com/test/rich-results                │ │                                                                              │ │  STEP 3: Deploy                                                             │ │     │                                                                        │ │     ├──► Ghost: Settings → Code Injection → Site Header                     │ │     ├──► WordPress: RankMath → Schema Templates                             │ │     ├──► Webflow: Page Settings → Custom Code → Head                        │ │     └──► Custom: <script type=\"application/ld+json\">                        │ │                                                                              │ │  STEP 4: Validate Live                                                      │ │     │                                                                        │ │     └──► Google Rich Results Test                                           │ │         └──► Schema Markup Validator                                        │ │             └──► Monitor Search Console for errors                          │ │                                                                              │ └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ Platform-Specific Implementation SOP Ghost Pro Implementation Step\tAction\tClick Location\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tTime 1\tOpen Ghost Admin\tyourdomain.com/ghost\tLogin credentials\tDashboard view\t30 sec 2\tNavigate to Code Injection\tSettings (gear icon) → Code injection\tNone\tCode editor opens\t10 sec 3\tPaste in Site Header\t\"Site Header\" text box\tYour JSON-LD wrapped in <script type=\"application/ld+json\"> tags\tCode saved\t1 min 4\tAdd per-post schema\tUse Ghost's custom excerpt + code injection per post\tArticle-specific JSON-LD\tIndividual post schema\t2 min/post 5\tSave and validate\tClick \"Save\" → Open Rich Results Test\tPublished page URL\tGreen checkmarks for valid schema\t2 min WordPress + RankMath Implementation Step\tAction\tClick Location\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tTime 1\tInstall RankMath\tPlugins → Add New → Search \"RankMath\"\tNone\tPlugin installed\t2 min 2\tRun Setup Wizard\tRankMath → Dashboard → Setup Wizard\tSite info, social profiles\tBase schema configured\t5 min 3\tConfigure Schema Templates\tRankMath → Titles & Meta → Posts/Pages\tSelect default schema type per content type\tAuto-applied schema\t3 min 4\tEdit individual schemas\tPost Editor → RankMath sidebar → Schema tab\tCustom fields per post\tEnhanced per-page schema\t2 min/post 5\tAdd custom schema\tRankMath → Schema → Custom Schema\tFull JSON-LD code\tAdvanced schema types added\t5 min Testing & Validation Tools Tool\tURL\tPurpose\tExpected Output Google Rich Results Test\tsearch.google.com/test/rich-results\tValidate schema renders correctly\tGreen checkmarks, preview of rich snippets Schema.org 